White Women is the fourth studio album by Chromeo, released on May 12, 2014 by Last Gang Records.

Chromeo singer Dave "Dave 1" Macklovitch felt like the duo "progressed more on this record, made a more ambitious, more accomplished, longer, more substantial album", adding, "There's more guitar, there's more bass, there are string arrangements; it feels more alive to me. I'm really happy for that."
